{"tid":380671,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先搭電梯有個臭閪港女以為我非禮佢，點知。。。","createTime":"2017-08-30T10:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T06:53:20.000Z","uid":43557,"like":176,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe069caa82b632eb937e79f522f89bc211578c7","tid":380671,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T10:08:46.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩搭完地鐵出去準備上電梯<br />\n我排係個臭閪港女後面<br />\n之後去到電梯口 有另一條女插左入黎<br />\n排係我同個港女中間<br />\n不過個港女應該唔知 以為我仲係佢後面<br />\n之後去到中段 唔知係咪因為中間條女攞野果陣唔小心掂倒佢屎忽<br />\n個港女即刻極速咁180度向後轉同時勁大聲咁講：「死變態佬！！！」<br />\n之後我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢見倒後面原來係條女黎既 個西樣即刻尷尬到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我忍撚住笑<br />\n之後上到去 佢後面條女大大聲同佢講左聲唔好意思再摺一聲就走左<br />\n其他人係後面都陰陰咀笑<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母呀臭閪港女咁鍾意屈人非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd7490a0497c5cb547a9ad601c44db3b19c73a8","tid":380671,"uid":50744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T10:09:26.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"643455e2ba76fc55cbdeed7ffe391d8db7e6e3a8","tid":380671,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T10:09:34.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87cea6a3007e09d55067187c26d888da581228d","tid":380671,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T10:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7030e29ae8ccda6213a13fa38722d1da1b51a9c","tid":380671,"uid":49058,"like":